\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf6 \strokec6 34 He went to him and bandaged his wounds, pouring on oil and wine. Then he put the man on his own donkey, brought him to an inn and took care of him.\'a0\'a0
\f1\fs24 \cf2 \strokec2 \
